Package com.versant.trans

Interface Summary
VEnumeration The VEnumeration Interface provides methods to manage a sequence of persistent objects that would be returned by a query.
 

Class Summary
Query The Query class defines a query in a single database.
QueryResult Instances of this class are created by the com.versant.trans.Query.execute() method.
TransSession The VERSANT/Java Transparent Session class.
VQLQuery VQLQuery -- implements queries with the Versant Query Language (VQL), which is a subset of OQLQuery specified in ODMG 2.0.
 

Exception Summary
VSchemaException A run-time exception that is thrown if the class in the database schema differs from the Java class at the transparent language binding layer.
